---
<Layout title="Booking & Appointment Websites with WordPress" description="Get an affordable WordPress booking website for your salon, tradie, or consulting business in Auckland. Accept bookings & payments online with Kiwi Web Design." schema={schema}>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">WordPress Services</p>
        <h1>Booking & Appointment Websites with WordPress</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Get an affordable WordPress booking website for your salon, tradie, or consulting business in Auckland. Accept bookings & payments online with Kiwi Web Design.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="/website-designer-auckland/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
          <a href="/small-business-website-design-auckland/#packages" class="btn-outline">View Packages</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-img">
        <img src="https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/booking-appointment-wordpress-auckland.jpg" alt="Booking & Appointment Websites with WordPress" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="prose">
<h2>Make it easy for your customers to book your services online.
Kiwi Web Design builds affordable and smart WordPress booking websites for salons, tradies, consultants, and service businesses across Auckland.</h2> 

<a href="/web-design-auckland/">
 
 Free Quote
 
 </a>

<img src="https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/booking-appointment-wordpress-auckland.jpg" alt="Online booking and appointment website for Auckland small businesses" loading="lazy"> 

<h3><strong>Why Every Small Business Needs an Online Booking System</strong></h3><p>If you’re running a salon, cleaning business, consultancy, or any service that relies on appointments — managing bookings manually can get messy. Missed calls, double bookings, and endless text confirmations can waste your time and cost you customers.</p><p>With a WordPress booking website, you can automate your appointments, send reminders, and take payments online — all while you focus on doing the work you love.</p><hr><h3><strong>Online Booking Solutions for Salons &amp; Beauty Businesses</strong></h3><p>Let your clients book their next haircut, facial, or massage anytime — even when you’re closed.<br>A WordPress booking system can:</p><ul><li><p>Show available time slots automatically</p></li><li><p>Send email/SMS reminders</p></li><li><p>Accept deposits or full payments upfront</p></li><li><p>Integrate with Google Calendar or Square</p></li></ul><p>That means fewer no-shows and a smoother client experience — perfect for busy Auckland beauty salons and spas.</p><hr><h3><strong>Appointment Websites for Tradies &amp; Home Services</strong></h3><p>Electricians, plumbers, cleaners, or lawn care pros — a booking website saves you hours each week.<br>Imagine clients booking their preferred date and time directly from your website. You get instant notifications, job details, and the ability to approve or reschedule with one click.</p><p>We can also set up quote request forms or service menus so clients know exactly what they’re booking.</p><hr><h3><strong>Consultants, Tutors &amp; Health Professionals</strong></h3><p>Whether you’re a business coach, personal trainer, or physiotherapist — booking automation means fewer emails back and forth.<br>You can offer:</p><ul><li><p>1-on-1 or group bookings</p></li><li><p>Paid sessions via Stripe or PayPal</p></li><li><p>Zoom/Google Meet integration</p></li><li><p>Automatic confirmations and follow-ups</p></li></ul><p>Your clients will appreciate the convenience, and you’ll save hours every week.</p><hr><h3><strong>Smart Features for Modern Businesses</strong></h3><p>Our WordPress booking websites include:</p><ul><li><p>Mobile-friendly calendars and dashboards</p></li><li><p>Automated reminders and cancellations</p></li><li><p>Integration with WooCommerce or Stripe</p></li><li><p>Dashboard analytics for appointments and revenue</p></li></ul><p>All set up so you can easily manage your business from your phone or laptop.</p><hr><h3><strong>Real Results for Auckland Businesses</strong></h3><p>Our clients report:</p><ul><li><p>40% fewer missed appointments</p></li><li><p>60% more repeat customers</p></li><li><p>100% more time to focus on their actual service</p></li></ul><p>No more messy spreadsheets or message trails — just a clean, automated system that works for you.</p><hr><h4><strong>Ready to grow your business with a smarter website?</strong></h4><p><br>At Kiwi Web Design, we build affordable, high-performing booking websites for Auckland businesses.<br><a href="/website-designer-auckland/">Contact us today</a> to get started.</p><blockquote><p>“We don’t just design your website — we set you up for ongoing success.”</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><strong>Related Services:</strong><br><a href="/affordable-web-design-auckland/">Affordable Web Design Auckland</a><br><a href="/web-designs-auckland/">Ecommerce Website Design Auckland</a><br><a href="/web-design-auckland/">Contact Kiwi Web Design</a></p></blockquote> 

<meta itemprop="serviceType" content="Booking & Appointment Websites with WordPress">
 <meta itemprop="provider" content="Kiwi Web Design">
 <meta itemprop="areaServed" content="Auckland, New Zealand">
 <table>
 <tr>
 <th>Feature</th>
 <th>Benefit</th>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td>Online Booking Calendar</td>
 <td>Customers can book anytime — even outside business hours.</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td>Automated Email & SMS Reminders</td>
 <td>Reduce no-shows and improve client reliability.</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td>Integrated Payments</td>
 <td>Take deposits or full payments via Stripe or WooCommerce.</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td>Calendar Sync</td>
 <td>Sync with Google Calendar or Outlook for instant updates.</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td>Mobile Friendly Dashboard</td>
 <td>Manage your bookings from your phone or laptop.</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td>Analytics & Reports</td>
 <td>Track appointments, revenue, and repeat customers easily.</td>
 </tr>
 </table>
 
 <a href="/website-designer-auckland/">Get a Free Quote</a>

<details>
 <summary>Can I take payments directly through my booking website?</summary>
 
 <p>Yes. Your WordPress booking site can connect to Stripe, PayPal, or WooCommerce to accept deposits or full payments during booking.</p>
 
</details>

<details>
 <summary>Is this suitable for salons and spas?</summary>
 
 <p>Absolutely. We’ve built many salon and spa websites that allow clients to choose services, staff, and time slots with automatic reminders and payments.</p>
 
</details>

<details>
 <summary>Can tradies use this to manage job bookings?</summary>
 
 <p>Yes. Tradies can let clients request times, confirm or reschedule jobs, and even sync appointments with their phone calendar.</p>
 
</details>

<details>
 <summary>What if I already have a website?</summary>
 
 <p>We can integrate a booking system into your existing WordPress website without rebuilding it from scratch.</p>
 
</details>

<details>
 <summary>Can I manage everything from my phone?</summary>
 
 <p>Yes. Your booking dashboard is mobile responsive, so you can confirm, cancel, or reschedule appointments on the go.</p>
 
</details>

<details>
 <summary>Do you provide training after setup?</summary>
 
 <p>We provide a short handover session to show you how to manage your calendar, notifications, and reports.</p>
 
</details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-strip">
    <h2>Ready to grow your business online?</h2>
    <p>Let's build something that works for you. Free consultation, no obligation.</p>
    <div class="cta-btns">
      <a href="/website-designer-auckland/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
      <a href="/small-business-website-design-auckland/#packages" class="btn-outline">View Our Packages</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── hero ── */
  .hero { background: var(--kwd-dark); color: var(--kwd-white); padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
  .hero-text { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--kwd-yellow); font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .6rem; }
  .hero-text h1 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.2; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.05rem; opacity: .85; max-width: 580px; margin: 0 0 2rem; line-height: 1.65; }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--kwd-yellow); color: var(--kwd-dark); padding: .75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-size: .95rem; }
  .btn-outline { border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6); color: var(--kwd-white); padding: .75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-size: .95rem; }
  .hero-img { flex: 0 0 42%; }
  .hero-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; object-fit: cover; max-height: 380px; display: block; }
  /* ── prose content ── */
  .page-content { padding: 3.5rem 0; }
  .prose { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .prose h1 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .prose h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.6rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 .75rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--kwd-yellow); padding-bottom: .3rem; }
  .prose h3 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 1.75rem 0 .5rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .prose h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 1.25rem 0 .4rem; color: #222; }
  .prose h5, .prose h6 { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 1rem 0 .35rem; color: #333; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #333; }
  .prose ul { padding-left: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; list-style: disc; }
  .prose ol { padding-left: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: .4rem; line-height: 1.65; color: #333; }
  .prose img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin: 1.75rem 0; display: block; }
  .prose blockquote { border-left: 4px solid var(--kwd-yellow); padding: .75rem 1.25rem; margin: 1.75rem 0; background: #f8f6f0; font-style: italic; color: #444; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; }
  .prose a { color: var(--kwd-dark); text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--kwd-brown); }
  .prose strong { color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .prose table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.75rem 0; font-size: .9rem; overflow-x: auto; display: block; }
  .prose th, .prose td { padding: .65rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: left; white-space: nowrap; }
  .prose th { background: var(--kwd-dark); color: var(--kwd-white); }
  .prose tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }
  /* ── faq ── */
  .faq-section { background: var(--kwd-cream); padding: 4rem 0; }
  .faq-inner { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .faq-inner > h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0 0 2rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #d8d0c0; }
  .faq-item summary { cursor: pointer; padding: 1.1rem 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--kwd-yellow); flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: .75rem; }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '−'; }
  .faq-answer { padding: .25rem 0 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #444; }
  .faq-answer p { margin: 0 0 .6rem; }
  .faq-answer ul, .faq-answer ol { padding-left: 1.3rem; margin: 0 0 .6rem; }
  /* ── cta ── */
  .cta-strip { background: var(--kwd-dark); color: var(--kwd-white); text-align: center; padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  .cta-strip h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
  .cta-strip p { opacity: .85; margin: 0 0 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .cta-btns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; justify-content: center; }
  /* ── contact form ── */
  .contact-section { padding: 4rem 0; background: var(--kwd-cream); }
  .contact-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .contact-inner h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0 0 .5rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .contact-inner > p { margin: 0 0 2rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.65; }
  .contact-form { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4rem; }
  .form-group label { font-weight: 600; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select { padding: .7rem 1rem; border: 2px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: inherit; background: #fff; transition: border-color .2s; }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--kwd-yellow); }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 130px; }
  .form-submit { margin-top: .5rem; }
  /* ── responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-inner { flex-direction: column; }
    .hero-img { display: none; }
    .hero-text h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  }
</style>
